column5: I live in south eastern NY. and are looking for a couple of people from the nearby area ,Conn, N.Jersey , SE Penn, who want to drive into a lake in N.Quebec and camp and fish for a week.I have most of the gear we need, tent, cook tent, boat, etc. If you are interested in doing this call me @347-640-2294 or 914-962-5842 thank you.
Curious where you are heading - sent you a pm. Thanks
